race.comment: TUB STAR (1) is better than last start when eighth (17.78) from Box 5 at this track over 300m. Has won two of four starts from this draw. Ready to return to form. OSCAR DUTTON (8) rocketed out of the inside draw with a strong early sectional and gave a sight but had to settle for a placing, finishing second (16.94) at this track over 300m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Will give a great sight again. ROBELL CLYDE (4) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (20.35) in a Free For All at Grafton. Form here sound including three wins. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Great chance to atone. LOONGANA LILLY (3) is always hard to beat when she races here at this trip.
